'''科孚海峽事件'''（{{lang-en|Corfu Channel incident}}）包括1946年在[[科孚海峡|科孚海峡]]发生的涉及[[英国皇家海军|英国皇家海军]]舰船的三个独立事件，被认为是[[冷战|冷战]]的早期事件之一<ref name="Journal of Legal History">[http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/journals/AJLH/2005/3.html Australian Journal of Legal History] {{Wayback|url=http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/journals/AJLH/2005/3.html |date=20170516120445 }} Half Light Between War and Peace: Herbert Vere Evatt, The Rule of International Law, and The Corfu Channel Case</ref><ref name="Corfu Incident">{{cite book |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title=Europe Since 1945: An Encyclopedia |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ox_gXq2jpdYC&pg=PA224&lpg=PA224&dq=Royal+Navy+Corfu+Channel&source=web&ots=nbpO3B4_Jz&sig=QUfXd2KWVSL-48YYLxyPxDjXdpc&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=4&ct=result |editor1-last=Cook |editor1-first=Bernard A. |chapter=Corfu Channel Incident |publisher=Taylor & Francis |year=2001 |isbn=978-0-8153-1336-6 |page=224 |volume=1 |access-date=23 April 2015 |archive-date=2015-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150322022405/http://books.google.com/books?id=ox_gXq2jpdYC&pg=PA224&lpg=PA224&dq=Royal+Navy+Corfu+Channel&source=web&ots=nbpO3B4_Jz&sig=QUfXd2KWVSL-48YYLxyPxDjXdpc&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=4&ct=result |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Timesonline">[http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/obituaries/article721285.ece Times Online] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/obituaries/article721285.ece |date=20110512175646 }} Obituary: Lieutenant-Commander Hugh Knollys Navigator who won a [[Distinguished_Service_Cross_(United_Kingdom)|DSC]] on [[D-Day|D-Day]] and survived when his destroyer hit a mine in the postwar Corfu Channel incident.</ref><ref name="Roselli">{{cite book |title=Italy and Albania: financial relations in the Fascist period |last=Roselli |first=Alessandro |authorlink= |author2= |year=2006 |publisher=I.B. Tauris |location= |isbn= |page= |pages=136–137 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Iv-iW3WGDvIC&pg=PA136&hl=en&ei=JsgCTKfuBcT7lwebv6miCA&sa=X&ved=0CDoQ6wEwBA#v=onepage |accessdate=30 May 2010 |archive-date=2014-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715055815/http://books.google.com/books?id=Iv-iW3WGDvIC&pg=PA136&hl=en&ei=JsgCTKfuBcT7lwebv6miCA&sa=X&ved=0CDoQ6wEwBA#v=onepage |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Waibel, Michael, (2012) ‘Corfu Channel Case’ in Rüdiger Wolfrum (ed), Max Planck Encyclopedia of Public International Law, vol III (Oxford University Press 2012), https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=1919599 {{Wayback|url=https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=1919599 |date=20200730052630 }}</ref>。在第一起事件中，皇家海军船只遭到[[阿尔巴尼亚|阿尔巴尼亚]]要塞炮击<ref name="Corfu Incident"/>。第二起事件中皇家海军触及了水雷，第三起事件发生在皇家海军在科孚海峡进行扫雷行动时进入阿尔巴尼亚领海<ref name="Journal of Legal History"/>，阿尔巴尼亚为此向[[联合国|联合国]]投诉<ref name="Corfu channel">[https://www.jstor.org/pss/2193642 JSTOR] {{Wayback|url=https://www.jstor.org/pss/2193642 |date=20210310225700 }} The Corfu Channel Case Quincy Wright The American Journal of International Law, Vol. 43, No. 3 (July 1949), pp. 491–494 (article consists of 4 pages) Published by: American Society of International Law Retrieved 31-07-08</ref>。

这一系列事件导致英国向国际法院提起了针对[[阿尔巴尼亚人民共和国|阿尔巴尼亚人民共和国]]的{{le|科孚海峡案|Corfu Channel case}}<ref name="Corfu channel" />。法院作出判决，阿尔巴尼亚将向英国支付844,00英镑，按2015年计算相当于3000万英镑的赔偿<ref name="Roselli" />。由于该事件，英国于1946年中断了与阿尔巴尼亚旨在建立两国之间的外交关系的对话。两国的外交关系直到1991年才恢复。

==历史==
{{expand section}}
[[File:HMS_Orion_(85).jpg|thumb]]

事件起源于1946年5月15日，两艘皇家海军舰船{{tsl|en|HMS Orion (85)|猎户座号轻巡洋舰}}和{{tsl|en|HMS Superb (25)|华丽号轻巡洋舰}}按照命令跨越并清理科孚海峽<ref name="Corfu Incident"/><ref name="ABC">[http://www.historyandtheheadlines.abc-clio.com/ContentPages/ContentPage.aspx?entryId=1162021&currentSection=1130228&productid=4 ABC CLIO Schools] {{Wayback|url=http://www.historyandtheheadlines.abc-clio.com/ContentPages/ContentPage.aspx?entryId=1162021&currentSection=1130228&productid=4 |date=20200510224325 }} Corfu Channel Incident (1946)</ref>。
在两艘轻巡洋舰跨越海峡时，受到了阿尔巴尼亚岸防堡垒炮兵的射击<ref name="Corfu Incident"/><ref name="Timesonline"/>。炮弹均未击中，英军也未回击。尽管英军舰船没有受到实质性损伤，也没有人员伤亡，英国仍通过正规的外交渠道要求阿尔巴尼亚政府公开致歉<ref name="Corfu Incident"/>。然而，类似的道歉在第一次海峡危机中并未出现，取而代之的是阿尔巴尼亚政府宣称英军入侵了阿尔巴尼亚海域<ref name="Corfu Incident"/><ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=T68DkhSaj8EC&pg=PA32&lpg=PA32&dq=Corfu+Channel+Incident&source=web&ots=jK0_a7h2tx&sig=1St9-nMC2vaBFxUxjt8tlLS7eAQ&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=9&ct=result Digest of International Cases on the Law of the Sea] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=T68DkhSaj8EC&pg=PA32&lpg=PA32&dq=Corfu+Channel+Incident&source=web&ots=jK0_a7h2tx&sig=1St9-nMC2vaBFxUxjt8tlLS7eAQ&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=9&ct=result |date=20191210224113 }} By Division for Ocean Affairs and the Law of the Sea, United Nations Division for Ocean Affairs and the Law of the Sea, [[聯合國法律事務廳|聯合國法律事務廳]] Published by [[联合国|联合国]], 2007 {{ISBN|978-92-1-133759-4}}. 272 pages</ref>。阿尔巴尼亚方认为，所有通过科孚海峡的船只均应向阿尔巴尼亚政府通报，否则阿尔巴尼亚军有权提前示警。英方则宣称阿尔巴尼亚军并未提前示警，并且威胁若英军再遭遇相同情况，英方有权回击<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.co.il/books?id=wiVzAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA237 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-08-26 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728200604/https://books.google.co.il/books?id=wiVzAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA237 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

第二次事件更加严重<ref name="Corfu Incident"/>。1946年10月22日，皇家海军的一支[[巡洋舰|巡洋舰]][[区舰队|分舰队]]被要求[[無害通過|無害通過]]科孚海峽，以测试阿尔巴尼亚人的反应<ref name="Journal of Legal History">[http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/journals/AJLH/2005/3.html Australian Journal of Legal History] Half Light Between War and Peace: Herbert Vere Evatt, The Rule of International Law, and The Corfu Channel Case</ref><ref name="ABC"/><ref name="ICJ">[http://www.iilj.org/courses/documents/CorfuChannel.pdf Institute for International Law and Justice] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091229215333/http://www.iilj.org/courses/documents/CorfuChannel.pdf |date=29 December 2009 }}</ref>，船员被命令，如果受到攻击那么可以还击<ref name="Journal of Legal History"/>。

